<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #333;">
  Dear <strong><%= name %></strong>,
</p>

<p
  style="
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.6;
  "
>
  Thanks for signing up for
  <span style="font-weight: bold; color: #007bff;">Nice App</span>. We're very
  excited to have you on board.
</p>

<p
  style="
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.6;
  "
>
  Here are your account details:
</p>

<ul
  style="
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding-left: 20px;
  "
>
  <li>
    Email: <span style="font-weight: bold; color: #007bff;"><%= email %></span>
  </li>
  <li>
    Login URL:
    <a href="<%= loginUrl %>" style="color: #007bff; text-decoration: none;"
      ><%= loginUrl %></a
    >
  </li>
</ul>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #333;">
  Thanks! <br />
  <span style="font-weight: bold;">NestJS Blog Support</span>
</p>
